Add gesture demo page and fix presentation viewer
Add a new demo page for gestures and integrate gesture detection with the presentation viewer.
* **Demo Page**: Add `app/demo/page.tsx` to showcase gesture functionalities. Import `GestureDetector` and `HandTracking` components. Add a container to display the gesture demo, a heading, a description, and a section to display detected gestures. * **Navigation**: Update `app/page.tsx` to include a link to the new demo page in the navigation. * **Presentation Viewer**: Modify `components/presentation/slide-viewer.tsx` to fix the presentation content display issue. Fetch and display the actual slide content based on `id` and `currentSlide`. Integrate gesture detection to allow gesture-based navigation and interaction. * **Gesture Detection**: Modify `components/gesture/gesture-detector.tsx` to add new gesture detection logic for "next" and "previous" gestures. Call the `onGesture` callback with the detected gesture. * **Hand Tracking**: Modify `components/gesture/hand-tracking.tsx` to add a new state to track the detected gesture and display the detected gesture on the video feed.
---
